						<div class="postbody">DMC will play any digitized sound you throw at it.  Give it a recording of a drum and it will play it.  It's how those baseball games on the NES yell out "Strike!" and "Ball!".
<br />Of course, first the sound gets converted to 1-bit, and gets sampled at a much lower rate.</div>

					
